                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200628-34-off189 t18200628-34-cd190"></join>, at St. Luke, Chelsea, one time-piece, value 8 l., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200628-34-victim373" type="victimName">
