                     <interp inst="t18200628-34-person377" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I apprehended the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18200628-34-person378">
                  MARIA 
                  MAY
               <interp inst="t18200628-34-person378" type="surname" value="MAY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200628-34-person378" type="given" value="MARIA"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200628-34-person378" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             re-examined. The time-piece cost 8 l. at a sale, five or six years ago - it was worth 4 l. It had a mahogany case, with four brass feet.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I have no friends, as I do not live in town.</p>
               <p>
